{
  "lesson": "WC-12-02",
  "audioMaster": "training/module12-settings/WC-12-02-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 269.871,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open Settings, and find the Locations group in the left rail.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.549,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Four pages live here.",
      "startS": 3.879,
      "endS": 5.244,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "One holds every site you run and everything hanging off it.",
      "startS": 5.606,
      "endS": 9.041,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "The other three group your sites, style what customers see, and guard the payment keys.",
      "startS": 9.435,
      "endS": 14.428,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "We'll read all four, and change none of them.",
      "startS": 14.712,
      "endS": 17.358,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Now open Locations.",
      "startS": 17.76,
      "endS": 19.434,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "A band of tiles reads the network at a glance: how many sites, how many active,",
      "startS": 20.091,
      "endS": 22.686,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "how many states, and when they last synced.",
      "startS": 23.004,
      "endS": 27.452,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Under it, three panels chart growth, split the sites by state,",
      "startS": 27.934,
      "endS": 28.354,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "and score how healthy their setup is.",
      "startS": 28.642,
      "endS": 30.108,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "This is your map before you open a single site.",
      "startS": 30.407,
      "endS": 34.046,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "And if the list underneath ever reads couldn't load,",
      "startS": 34.547,
      "endS": 37.302,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "that's the agent service dropping, not an empty tenant.",
      "startS": 37.803,
      "endS": 43.911,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Look at the list itself.",
      "startS": 44.496,
      "endS": 46.313,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Eight columns, and the one that matters most is Code.",
      "startS": 46.313,
      "endS": 49.074,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "That short site code follows a location through every screen in the platform,",
      "startS": 49.074,
      "endS": 53.152,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "so learn to read it first.",
      "startS": 53.152,
      "endS": 54.808,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Search by name or code up top, filter beside it, and leave New Record alone.",
      "startS": 54.808,
      "endS": 59.757,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Last Sync on the right tells you when the site last checked in,",
      "startS": 59.757,
      "endS": 63.759,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "which is the first thing you read when a site looks silent.",
      "startS": 63.759,
      "endS": 67.071,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Click a site to open it.",
      "startS": 67.52,
      "endS": 68.865,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "One location, five tabs.",
      "startS": 70.172,
      "endS": 72.04,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "Profile, Operations, Payments and Credentials, Messaging, and Users.",
      "startS": 72.432,
      "endS": 74.152,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "That strip is the whole record,",
      "startS": 74.387,
      "endS": 75.592,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "and every support question about a site starts by picking the right tab.",
      "startS": 75.808,
      "endS": 77.379,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Profile is where you land.",
      "startS": 77.84,
      "endS": 85.99,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Start with Profile.",
      "startS": 86.56,
      "endS": 87.961,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "This is who and where: the site's code and name, its address, its contact details, its hours.",
      "startS": 88.424,
      "endS": 90.065,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "When a ticket names a location you don't recognize,",
      "startS": 90.311,
      "endS": 94.909,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "this tab confirms you're looking at the right one before you touch anything else.",
      "startS": 95.544,
      "endS": 102.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Now Operations.",
      "startS": 103.28,
      "endS": 103.965,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "This tab runs the site's behavior and its time clock.",
      "startS": 103.965,
      "endS": 107.983,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "Whether it shows on dashboards, whether it takes online orders,",
      "startS": 107.983,
      "endS": 111.991,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "and the rules that clock staff out and pay overtime.",
      "startS": 111.991,
      "endS": 116.154,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Find the automatic clock-out timeout and the overtime threshold,",
      "startS": 116.154,
      "endS": 119.237,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "read them, and leave them exactly as they are.",
      "startS": 119.237,
      "endS": 122.32,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Open Payments and Credentials.",
      "startS": 122.72,
      "endS": 124.564,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Below the portal and auto-charge options sits Credential Configuration,",
      "startS": 125.528,
      "endS": 133.101,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "split into a block for each processor a site can run:",
      "startS": 133.572,
      "endS": 134.226,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "Open Edge, Smart Tech, Other, and Card Connect.",
      "startS": 134.561,
      "endS": 135.282,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Every secret shows masked.",
      "startS": 135.724,
      "endS": 137.402,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Your job is to name which block is present, never to read the value.",
      "startS": 138.351,
      "endS": 140.012,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "For a decline ticket, the gateway name is all support needs.",
      "startS": 140.293,
      "endS": 148.64,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "Two tabs left. Messaging.",
      "startS": 149.114,
      "endS": 150.086,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "This holds the messages a site sends on its own, set per location rather than network-wide.",
      "startS": 150.625,
      "endS": 151.364,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "When a customer at one site gets a text that another site's customers don't, this tab is why.",
      "startS": 151.854,
      "endS": 162.454,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "You read what's set here; you send nothing.",
      "startS": 162.718,
      "endS": 165.152,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Then Users.",
      "startS": 165.6,
      "endS": 166.905,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "This is who can work this site.",
      "startS": 167.442,
      "endS": 169.05,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "When someone says they can't get into a location, check here before you reset anything:",
      "startS": 169.597,
      "endS": 174.105,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "they may simply not be assigned to it.",
      "startS": 174.416,
      "endS": 176.387,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "Read the list; open nothing.",
      "startS": 176.838,
      "endS": 178.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Back out with the Back button.",
      "startS": 179.28,
      "endS": 180.764,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Nothing saved, nothing changed.",
      "startS": 181.324,
      "endS": 183.269,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "And even if you wanted to swap a site's credentials, you couldn't finish it here:",
      "startS": 183.832,
      "endS": 187.737,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "those changes route to an approval queue, which is the next page we read.",
      "startS": 188.227,
      "endS": 192.16,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Open Location Groups.",
      "startS": 192.64,
      "endS": 194.302,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "A group bundles several sites so a report or a dashboard treats them as one.",
      "startS": 195.506,
      "endS": 200.176,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "Five columns: the name, a description, how many sites it holds,",
      "startS": 200.837,
      "endS": 201.709,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "its geo group, and whether it shows on the dashboard.",
      "startS": 202.016,
      "endS": 206.115,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p61",
      "text": "Read only.",
      "startS": 206.444,
      "endS": 209.085,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p62",
      "text": "Next, Location Sub-Brand.",
      "startS": 209.577,
      "endS": 211.699,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p63",
      "text": "The link says Sub-Brand, the page says Sub-Brands, same place.",
      "startS": 212.456,
      "endS": 213.799,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p64",
      "text": "This styles the customer-facing panels, the panel type and the colors,",
      "startS": 214.045,
      "endS": 216.745,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p65",
      "text": "so one operator can run sites under more than one look.",
      "startS": 217.405,
      "endS": 224.837,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p66",
      "text": "Last page: Payment Credential Approval.",
      "startS": 225.28,
      "endS": 226.102,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p67",
      "text": "This is where those credential changes land for sign-off.",
      "startS": 226.48,
      "endS": 227.939,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p68",
      "text": "Each row shows a location, its gateway, and a status: pending, approved, or rejected.",
      "startS": 228.414,
      "endS": 230.871,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p69",
      "text": "In the capture, two sites sat approved on Open Edge.",
      "startS": 231.505,
      "endS": 235.01,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p70",
      "text": "When an admin says a site's new keys aren't live yet, this status column is your answer,",
      "startS": 235.363,
      "endS": 237.416,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p71",
      "text": "one pending row and you know it's still in the queue.",
      "startS": 238.049,
      "endS": 249.44,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p72",
      "text": "So that's the Locations area.",
      "startS": 249.84,
      "endS": 251.58,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p73",
      "text": "One list, one five-tab record, three sibling pages.",
      "startS": 251.968,
      "endS": 254.243,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p74",
      "text": "The site list gets you in,",
      "startS": 254.492,
      "endS": 255.823,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p75",
      "text": "the tabs tell you who, how, and with which processor,",
      "startS": 256.03,
      "endS": 257.786,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p76",
      "text": "and the sibling pages bundle sites, style them, and sign off their credentials.",
      "startS": 258.011,
      "endS": 266.192,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s14",
      "id": "p77",
      "text": "You read all of it, and you change none of it.",
      "startS": 266.619,
      "endS": 269.439,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}